Units #1 & 2 were eastbound on Master St. with a green traffic signal at 52nd St. Unit #1 made a right turn to southbound 52nd St. when it struck Unit #2, who was in the south crosswalk of the intersection of 52nd St. and Master St. Unit #2 was pronounced dead at Penn Presbyterian Medical Center a short time later.
